article.description: — Tristen Newton recorded 14 points and 10 assists to lift East Carolina to a 65-57 win over South Florida on Thursday night.
article.headline: Newton carries East Carolina over South Florida 65-57
article.linkText: Newton carries East Carolina over South Florida 65-57
article.story: TAMPA, Fla. -- — Tristen Newton recorded 14 points and 10 assists to lift East Carolina to a 65-57 win over South Florida on Thursday night. Vance Jackson had 16 points for East Carolina (13-12, 4-9 American Athletic Conference). Brandon Suggs added 13 points and Tremont Robinson-White had 10 points and six rebounds. Serrel Smith Jr. had 18 points for the Bulls (7-18, 2-11), whose losing streak stretched to four games. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
